title: El Dandy
typeOfFood: Salad bar, Juice bar, Beer/Wine, Mexican, Spanish, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cozy small bar/bistro serving tropical juices, fresh salads and vegetables like avocado and pimientos and vegan soup like gazpacho. Does offer a small choice of snacks with meat or cheese. As of October 2015, it's hard to find any vegan or vegetarian food in the old town of Habana. Nostalgic atmosphere.
